      "html": "<section class='cv'><div class='cv__media'><img src='https://img.youtube.com/vi/bNpx7gpSqbY/maxresdefault.jpg' alt='Bill Gross speaking on a TED stage' /></div><div class='cv__veil'></div><div class='cv__grain'></div><div class='cv__tag cv__tag--left'>[richesse.club]</div><div class='cv__tag cv__tag--right'>[Bill Gross]</div><div class='cv__content'><h1 class='cv__title'><span>스타트업의 승패는</span><span>아이디어보다</span><span>타이밍이 먼저 가른다</span></h1><p class='cv__deck'>The single biggest reason why start-ups succeed</p></div></section>",
